{"tid":1471196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續衝入機場阻人啦！害群之馬","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T13:26:49.000Z","uid":288154,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b12ab6747290bc5d98504dc27649b93fa31243d5","tid":1471196,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:11:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">唔好再問我係咪割，同割唔割無關，只因我係完全理性，不能作不合情理嘅事！</span><br />\n<br />\n每次<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非</span>攞到十分成功成績嘅地方，<br />\n就有班<span style=\"color: red;\">害群之馬</span>嚟攪爛攪臭個場，<br />\n最後重引到防暴警有機會入機場拉人。<br />\n<br />\n一連四日和理非佔盡優勢，第五日班害群之馬就入嚟攪，<br />\n今日機場只得三分一人喇！<br />\n<br />\n先不合作塞鐵阻乘客，令乘客失去<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人權</span></strong>已証明一錯。<br />\n再阻塞遊客入禁區上機，令遊客失去<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人權</span></strong>係極大錯。<br />\n人權係所有民主運動嘅基石，不專重人權嘅人實在無資格參與民主運動？！<br />\n<br />\n令運動焦點散曬，轉十幾個彎奢望間接再間接影響政府。<br />\n做出不合理嘅事，以為要人理解就可以推責任在政府身上，實在係自欺欺人！<br />\n<br />\n傳媒網台直播，<span style=\"color: red;\">有片有真相</span>，親政權派必會到區選時大做文章，結果區議會選舉我無眼睇喇！"},{"pid":"1fd668a8b0faa55a6508a2e93a4a5f9d32aef470","tid":1471196,"uid":205247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:11:37.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n借一借位sor<br />\n<br />\n［麻煩大家幫幫手］救救第一城！第一城不是集中營！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1471141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1471141</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"268b8d89c24350c52267857ad6c752ab116ed3b7","tid":1471196,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-t